languages.text: "В таком случае, этих паразитов надо поскорее извести. Я никогда не был в нижних секторах, но, уверен, простое население очень страдает от такого омерзительного соседства".

traits.locale_text: [Draft] Не знаю, я редко покдаю дворец и никогда не спускался на нижние уровни, даже не представляю как там живет чернь, наверно тяжело

languages.text: "In that case, these parasites must be done away with post-haste. I've never been to the lower sectors, but I'm sure the common people suffer greatly from such loathsome neighbours."

languages.text: “如果是这种情况，那这些寄生虫必须尽快处理掉。虽然我从来没去过下层区域，但我很确定，这群令人厌恶的邻居会导致普通人深受其害。”
languages.original_text: "In that case, these parasites must be done away with post-haste. I've never been to the lower sectors, but I'm sure the common people suffer greatly from such loathsome neighbours."

traits.locale_text: “如果是这种情况，那这些寄生虫必须尽快处理掉。虽然我从来没去过下层区域，但我很确定，这群令人厌恶的邻居会导致普通人深受其害。”

languages.text: «En ese caso, debemos eliminar a los parásitos cuanto antes. Nunca he estado en los sectores inferiores, pero supongo que la gente común sufre enormemente con unos vecinos tan deleznables».
languages.original_text: "In that case, these parasites must be done away with post-haste. I've never been to the lower sectors, but I'm sure the common people suffer greatly from such loathsome neighbours."

traits.locale_text: «En ese caso, debemos eliminar a los parásitos cuanto antes. Nunca he estado en los sectores inferiores, pero supongo que la gente común sufre enormemente con unos vecinos tan deleznables».

languages.text: 「それなら、こういう寄生虫は急いで始末しないとな。下層星域に行ったことはないが、こんな忌まわしい生き物が隣人とは、一般市民はとても苦しんでいることだろう」
languages.original_text: "In that case, these parasites must be done away with post-haste. I've never been to the lower sectors, but I'm sure the common people suffer greatly from such loathsome neighbours."

traits.locale_text: 「それなら、こういう寄生虫は急いで始末しないとな。下層星域に行ったことはないが、こんな忌まわしい生き物が隣人とは、一般市民はとても苦しんでいることだろう」

languages.text: "In dem Fall müssen diese Parasiten schnellstens entfernt werden. Ich war noch nie in den unteren Sektoren, aber ich bin sicher, die normalen Bürger leiden sehr unter solch abstoßenden Nachbarn."
languages.original_text: "In that case, these parasites must be done away with post-haste. I've never been to the lower sectors, but I'm sure the common people suffer greatly from such loathsome neighbours."

traits.locale_text: "In dem Fall müssen diese Parasiten schnellstens entfernt werden. Ich war noch nie in den unteren Sektoren, aber ich bin sicher, die normalen Bürger leiden sehr unter solch abstoßenden Nachbarn."

languages.text: « Dans ce cas, nous devons nous occuper de ces parasites au plus vite. Je n'ai jamais visité les secteurs inférieurs, mais je parie que les gens du commun souffrent grandement d'avoir des voisins aussi odieux. »
languages.original_text: "In that case, these parasites must be done away with post-haste. I've never been to the lower sectors, but I'm sure the common people suffer greatly from such loathsome neighbours."

languages.text: "O hâlde bu parazitlerin derhâl ortadan kaldırılması icap eder. Alt sektörlerde hiç bulunmadım ama eminim ki sıradan insanlar, böylesi iğrenç komşularından çok muzdariptir."
